 tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/siteground\/\" target=\"_blank\">Siteground<\/a> is our number one choice to host a WordPress blog. 24\/7 support and a super-easy WordPress installation without having to work in difficult codes. And a free domain name registration is included.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>More about:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/siteground\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"&#x27B3; More about: Hosting at Siteground (opens in a new tab)\">Hosting at Siteground<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image nopin\"><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/2-start-a-travel-blog-hosting.jpg\" alt=\"start a travel blog hosting\" class=\"wp-image-11986\"><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"wordpress\">3. Install WordPress to start a travel blog<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"http:\/\/wordpress.org\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress<\/a> is made for blogging. It is safe, self-updating, flexible if you need to, and future-proof. Once you&#x2019;ve signed up at <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Siteground (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/siteground\/\" target=\"_blank\">Siteground<\/a> click through the simple installation process on your Siteground cPanel. When it asks you where you&#x2019;d like to install it, choose your new domain (example: http:\/\/mytravelblog.com).<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Once installed, you&#x2019;ll be able to log into the WordPress dashboard with your new username and password.<br>Congratulations! You have now started a travel blog. That wasn&#x2019;t too hard, right? But wait, there&#x2019;s more!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/become-digital-nomad\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">How to Travel &amp; Work as a Digital Nomad<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/3-start-a-travel-blog-install-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"start a travel blog install wordpress\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"start a travel blog install wordpress\" class=\"wp-image-11987 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142609\/3-start-a-travel-blog-install-wordpress.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142609\/3-start-a-travel-blog-install-wordpress-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142609\/3-start-a-travel-blog-install-wordpress-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142609\/3-start-a-travel-blog-install-wordpress-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.sa