e. They will help you to use features made by the community, you developers all over the world. Start a travel blog well by installing the following plugins. Head over to your Dashboard &#x2013; Plugins &#x2013; Add new.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>Yoast SEO<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Search for Yoast SEO and click on install once you&#x2019;ve found it. This plugin will give all the SEO features a blogger can wish for. Including an SEO strength check when you are writing a new article.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image nopin\"><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/5-start-a-travel-blog-yoast-seo.jpg\" alt=\"start a travel blog yoast seo\" class=\"wp-image-11988\"><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>Easy Social Share Buttons<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Your hard-working articles need to be read by others. Start your travel blog traffic by installing the &#x2018;Easy Social Share Buttons&#x2019; plugin to add some excellent share options for your articles.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/start-a-travel-blog-social-buttons.jpg\" alt=\"start a travel blog social buttons\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"start a travel blog social buttons\" class=\"wp-image-12019 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142518\/start-a-travel-blog-social-buttons.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142518\/start-a-travel-blog-social-buttons-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142518\/start-a-travel-blog-social-buttons-600x400.jpg 600w, htt