Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"blog\">9. Creating your first blog article<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Start your first travel blog article, it can be about anything. For example, tell people why you are starting a travel blog, share what you&#x2019;re packing for an upcoming trip or write about the highlights from your last journey. Whatever the topic is, writing an article will help you understand how to publish images, write headers, and all the other formatting that comes with publishing on WordPress.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>See:<\/strong> <a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#masterclass\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Masterclass blogging<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/9-start-a-travel-blog-first-blog.jpg\" alt=\"start a travel blog first blog\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"286\" alt=\"start a travel blog first blog\" class=\"wp-image-11991 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142555\/9-start-a-travel-blog-first-blog.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142555\/9-start-a-travel-blog-first-blog-300x191.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23142555\/9-start-a-travel-blo