\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The hardest part of starting a travel blog or any kind of website is getting constant visitors. It could take months, or years to get a good number of visitors each day. Apply the following 4 methods correctly to start seeing traffic on your blog.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>Start a Travel blog: Google traffic<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Google Search is one of the best ways to generate traffic. However, getting your blog between those Google Search results is one of the hardest things in this world. You need to apply all the SEO rules, post consistently, have a well-functioning website and so many other things. Obviously, you can&#x2019;t do everything right but at least try the best you can. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"seo\">SEO &#x2013; What&#x2019;s SEO?<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO stands for Search Engine Optimisation, in other words,&#xA0;getting readers to your&#xA0;travel blog. Search engines like Google rate your website&#x2019;s SEO score by comparing it against a massive list of rules. The Yoast SEO helps you with the first steps. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>See:<\/strong> <a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#masterclass\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Masterclass blogging<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4><strong>Consistenc<\/strong>y<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>It took saltinourhair.com over 5 months over weekly posting to see a growth in visitors. Therefore it worked quite discouraging when we did not see readers reading our blogs. The key is to keep posting consequent and try to improve every new article.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Get to know<\/strong>: our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/work-from-home-effectively\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"14 Tips to Work from Home effectively (opens in a new tab)\">14 Tips to Work from Home effectively<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/start-a-travel-blog-google.jpg\" alt=\"start a travel blog google\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"start a travel blog google\" class=\"wp-image-9911 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/23150443\/start-a-travel-blog-google.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/23150443\/start-a-travel-blog-google-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/23150443\/start-a-travel-blog-google-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/23150443\/start-a-travel-blog-google-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/201